Bangchak Corporation Public Company Limited Key Developments

Bangchak Corporation Public Company Limited, Board Meeting, Jul 19, 2017
Jul 20 17
Bangchak Corporation Public Company Limited, Board Meeting, Jul 19, 2017. Agenda: To approve an amalgamation between BBP Holding Company Limited (BBH) and KSLGI Company Limited (KSLGI).


Bangchak Corporation Public Company Limited Announces Change in Directorship of Pichai Chunhavajira from Chairman and Non-Executive Director to Chairman and Independent Director
Jun 1 17
Bangchak Corporation Public Company Limited informed that the directorship of Mr. Pichai Chunhavajira is changed from "Chairman and Non-Executive Director" to "Chairman and Independent Director" effective from June 1, 2017.


Bangchak Corporation Public Company Limited Reports Unaudited Consolidated and Company Earnings Results for the First Quarter Ended March 31, 2017
May 8 17
Bangchak Corporation Public Company Limited reported unaudited consolidated and company earnings results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2017. For the quarter, on consolidated basis, the company reported revenue from sale of goods and rendering of services of THB 43,994,881,042 against THB 30,275,996,717 a year ago. EBITDA was THB 4,075 million against THB 1,419 million a year ago. Profit before finance cost and income tax expense was THB 3,034,651,940 against THB 401,428,121 a year ago. Profit before income tax expense was THB 2,679,851,122 against THB 28,545,069 a year ago. Profit attributable to the owners of the company was THB 2,083,808,821 against THB 268,890,200 a year ago. Earnings per share were THB 1.51 against THB 0.20 a year ago. Cash received from operating activities was THB 1,282,526,804 against THB 6,037,121,196 a year ago. Net cash paid for the purchase of intangible assets was THB 271,802,039 against THB 111,973,567 a year ago. Return on equity was 17.02% against 9.68% a year ago. Return on assets was 10.28% against 6.36% a year ago. Investment in property, plant and equipment was THB 1,227,689,567 against THB 1,968,554,977 a year ago, an investment in refinery machinery and equipment, marketing and office equipment of the company was THB 713 million, an investment in Biodiesel plant machinery and equipment was THB 181 million, construction work in progress in solar power plant of BCPG Plc. of THB 321 million.

For the quarter, on company basis, the company reported the company reported revenue from sale of goods and rendering of services of THB 41,168,199,822 against THB 28,519,994,451 a year ago. Profit before finance cost and income tax expense was THB 2,666,124,650 against loss of THB 152,615,610 a year ago. Profit before income tax expense was THB 2,426,956,950 against loss of THB 494,793,017 a year ago. Profit attributable to the owners of the company was THB 1,944,077,104 against loss of THB 357,365,945 a year ago. Earnings per share were THB 1.41 against loss per share of THB 0.26 a year ago. Cash received from operating activities was THB 912,479,084 against THB 5,523,661,002 a year ago. Acquisition of property, plant and equipment was THB 654,810,477 against THB 1,233,887,837 a year ago. Cash paid for the purchase of intangible assets was THB 3,596,548 against THB 114,143,581 a year ago.


