										Description
									

										BANGCHAK HDO HIGH LUBE  is a premium-quality hydraulic oil anti-wear type made from of selected and carefully refined high-quality base stocks incorporating additives to improve the anti-wear, lubricity, load-carrying, corrosion resistance, oxidation stability and separation/foaming propreties.  Excellent filterablity, demulsification of water and high viscosity index allow operation under adverse condition and assure long oil service life. 
									












